Tap to copy a permalink! Permalink for sharing! March 22, 2017 
We're just about sold out of London BAHFest tickets . Today is the last day I can guarantee any type of ticket, so please buy soon if you're planning to go! Discuss this comic in the forum March 21, 2017 
We're almost sold out ! Just a few days left to buy, if we don't sell out by tomorrow. See you soon, geeks of London! Discuss this comic in the forum March 20, 2017 
3/4 of all BAHFest London tickets are gone! Today we'll achieve 5/6, then after that 6/7, until we asymptotically approach a sold out show. Discuss this comic in the forum March 19, 2017 
Hey London nerds! We've got just about 60 student tickets left for BAHFest London, and then they're all gone!
